{"tid":1523322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥個仔 Email係ylam@math.harvard.edu","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:04:17.000Z","uid":212051,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1db52de27c927be6b5da002fa521ee77a8944b","tid":1523322,"uid":212051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥個仔 Joshua Lam 喺哈佛大學資料喺度，佢個Email係ylam@math.harvard.edu，而Linkedin就呢度！！！<br />\n<br />\n你想同佢講道理，可以send email俾佢，質問佢阿媽點解可以喪盡天良，指示警察對香港年青人開槍，佢作為一個年青人有乜感想。佢唔好話乜嘢唔識政治，呢啲唔係政治，係人性。但如果你係道理都費時講，將呢堆嘢交俾Donald Trump，其實根據美國現有法律，無香港人權及民主法，因為開咗槍，已經可以趕呢條友出去。讀乜嘢哈佛大學數學博士，呢啲學位留番俾其他家人係真心信奉民主自由嘅數學家，呢啲人讀個數學學位都唔知會做啲乜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/27260/林鄭月娥-你投共嘅代價就你家人承擔/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F27260%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E4%BD%A0%E6%8A%95%E5%85%B1%E5%98%85%E4%BB%A3%E5%83%B9%E5%B0%B1%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94%2Famp&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=55f173b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/27260/林鄭月娥-你投共嘅代價就你家人承擔/amp</a>"},{"pid":"2fe9619e122c8f4fc05d7ce560d51200d48410d5","tid":1523322,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:40:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eeb5d8c55d1343c83f9320ea9119827c4cc28327","tid":1523322,"uid":290836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f5124168ae58c36558408596dd02e18e468a4da8","tid":1523322,"uid":189596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f744fcef352d72cd22fa6f756cc8aec7425d57a7","tid":1523322,"uid":47081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:48:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16d115c84a910365417afef4af89701f21455c14","tid":1523322,"uid":202706,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08